lead_paragraph: A couple of days before she returned to the site of her stunning upset of Serena Williams at the 2015 U.S. Open, Roberta Vinci was grabbing a coffee at a Starbucks in Manhattan when her breakfast was interrupted by fellow customers.

headline.print_headline: Year After Stunning Williams, Vinci Returns to Open With Win
